{"tid":2096053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎智英都叫人走","createTime":"2020-07-06T02:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T05:53:27.000Z","uid":137088,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3e8400a9699b88b9ccd062ff1abb357a25804fba","tid":2096053,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:00:32.000Z","msg":"把我們驚醒的是突如其來的國安法，夢不瞬間崩塌，明天會是一場場的離別，不用糾纏，我也不打擾你們了。我心裏有驅不散的惆悵，原來以為煲底見。但人生太短暫，你們的時光走得太匆忙，路還未走完，心就老了，瞬間顏容已滄桑，太累了吧，也許你們做的已足夠。艷陽影樹紅花飄搖，趁景色還美麗，時光還和煦，騰出雙手擁抱自己，慶幸你們貢獻過，你們做的已足夠，不用回頭望了，向前走吧。昨天已過去，過去不該是將來的包袱，前面有太陽花海的燦爛等你們。讓傷心煩惱離去，不，你們還年輕，有一雙飛翔的翅膀，還等甚麼，飛吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎智英"},{"pid":"bb62bd582bfd968909e3b440b58b3d23fa3964fd","tid":2096053,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:02:39.000Z","msg":"要走快鳩D走，唔洗開POST話比人地知<br />\n<br />\n煩到閪咁"},{"pid":"856a4b4252039140f8d07b10ef79565e6e054154","tid":2096053,"uid":291487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:03:24.000Z","msg":"我想問source 呢"},{"pid":"bc56d4c6794597cc8e98f08d3524c8b820dc566b","tid":2096053,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:07:36.000Z","msg":"冇source冇link學咩人出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be64ae5efcb80ef04a2e8920186bdd2d156fef2","tid":2096053,"uid":74622,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:11:02.000Z","msg":"今天我瞪開眼睛一覺醒來。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英"},{"pid":"1242d8ca215ee03d02951fb70cd28939680f04dc","tid":2096053,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:18:46.000Z","msg":"香港民主之父<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ee36663b296d76e61008aedf2c3f452d364537","tid":2096053,"uid":392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:26:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1/daily/article/20200705/20949708\" 